no proof of UK address.","fix":"Tenancy agreement, council tax, photos of property","severity":"Common"},{"title":"English requirement missed","description":"No A1 SELT when required.","fix":"Book UKVI-approved SELT early","severity":"Common"},{"title":"Prior refusals undisclosed","description":"Hidden UK or immigration refusals.","fix":"Full disclosure with changed circumstances","severity":"High"}],"faqs":[{"q":"Can we guarantee spouse visa approval?","a":"No. UKVI assesses financial, relationship, and eligibility criteria. Genuine marriages can still face refusals if evidence is weak."},{"q":"What is minimum income requirement?","a":"Threshold changes with policy—verify current amount on gov.uk Appendix FM. Can combine salaried/non-salaried income or use savings alternative."},{"q":"Can savings substitute income?","a":"Yes, if meeting specified savings amount held for required period. Calculate per gov.uk guidance."},{"q":"How long until ILR?","a":"Typically 5 years on spouse route (with extensions). Verify current ILR rules and English requirements at each stage."},{"q":"Can spouse work in UK?","a":"Yes, generally no work restrictions on spouse visa—verify conditions on grant letter."},{"q":"Is marriage in India recognised?","a":"Yes if legally valid. Provide marriage certificate; certified translation if not in English."},{"q":"What if sponsor is on benefits?","a":"Some benefits count toward income; others don''t. Check permitted income sources on gov.uk."},{"q":"TB test required?","a":"Yes for Indian applicants from approved clinic before application."},{"q":"What is Description for this service?","a":"Family visa for spouse, civil partner, or unmarried partner of British citizen or person with settled/pre-settled status in UK. Leads to ILR pathway after qualifying period."},{"q":"What is Eligible applicants for this service?","a":"Valid marriage/civil partnership or 2+ years cohabitation · Sponsor meets financial requirement · Adequate accommodation · English A1 (entry) · Genuine relationship"},{"q":"What is Financial requirement for this service?","a":"Sponsor must meet minimum income threshold or qualify via savings. Rules updated periodically—verify current threshold on gov.uk."},{"q":"Important note on Financial requirement?","a":"Sponsor must meet minimum income threshold or qualify via savings. Rules updated periodically—verify current threshold on gov.uk."},{"q":"What is Key authority for this service?","a":"UK Visas and Immigration (UKVI) — Home Office"},{"q":"What is After approval for this service?","a":"Initial visa typically 33 months (if applying from outside UK); extension and ILR pathway. Maintain genuine relationship and comply with conditions."},{"q":"Is Sponsor is British citizen or settled/pre-settled required?","a":"Sponsor is British citizen or settled/pre-settled is typically required."},{"q":"Is Valid marriage or qualifying relationship required?","a":"Marriage cert or 2+ years cohabitation proof"},{"q":"Is Financial requirement met required?","a":"Income or savings per Appendix FM"},{"q":"Is Adequate accommodation in UK required?","a":"Tenancy or ownership evidence"},{"q":"Is English A1 (entry clearance) required?","a":"SELT or exempt nationality"},{"q":"Is TB test (if from listed country) required?","a":"India requires approved clinic test"},{"q":"Is Genuine relationship evidence required?","a":"Genuine relationship evidence is typically required."},{"q":"What is the Processing time?","a":"12–24w — Outside UK entry clearance"},{"q":"What is the Government fee?","a":"£1,846 — + IHS (5 years typical)"},{"q":"What is the Our approval rate?","a":"90% — ~80% industry benchmark"},{"q":"What is the Required docs?","a":"19 — + financial & relationship"},{"q":"What is the Consultancy fee?","a":"See fee tab — + govt & IHS"},{"q":"What if the client has Financial requirement not met?","a":"Calculate on gov.uk; combine permitted income sources or use savings route"},{"q":"Why is Financial requirement not me